  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink41-kilavi">kaḻaṟit teruṭṭaṟ pālarākiya akampukal marapiṉ vāyilkaḷ pukuntuḻit
          talaivaṉaiyum pāṇaṉ mutalākiya pakkattāraiyum ikaḻntu talaivi kūṟiyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink41">
          <l> taṉpārpput tiṉṉu maṉpiṉ mutalaiyoṭu</l>
          <l>veṇpūm poykait tavaṉū reṉpa ataṉāṟ</l>
          <l>ṟaṉco luṇarntōr mēṉi</l>
          <l>poṉpōṟ ceyyu mūrkiḻa vōṉē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l>There is a pond in his village with white flowers [in it]</l>
          <l>and crocodiles without hearts that eat their own young, they say.</l>
          <l>That is why he,</l>
          <l>the lord of the village,</l>
          <l>turns to gold </l>
          <l>the bodies of those women who perceived his words (OR took his words to heart).</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
